data.description: Brand New Roof in June 2023! Welcome to this stunning real estate opportunity! This exquisite home boasts three spacious bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms. The expansive family room offers a perfect space for gatherings and relaxation, while the office provides a dedicated area for productivity and focus. Situated conveniently, this charming residence is near a wide array of amenities. Indulge in the culinary delights of nearby restaurants and enjoy the convenience of shopping options just moments away. Nature enthusiasts will delight in the nearby park, complete with walking trails. Stay active and refreshed with access to a swimming pool and tennis courts, ensuring a vibrant and active lifestyle. Don't let this opportunity slip away. Become the proud owner of this captivating home, where comfort, convenience, and community converge. Schedule a viewing today and embark on a journey toward owning a truly remarkable piece of real estate.
